channel.title: VNV Nation new album
channel.description:
Not sure if any of you like VNV or even the type of music they and other bands do, but in case you do, a new album just came out : ) and while the following song isn´t the single from the album (Control is) I think it should´ve been so here it is : )
[url='https://youtu.be/On53QnYu9FA']VNV Nation - Nova[/url]
